abilities</h2>Use your abilities on your adventure to get the best out of the capabilities of your ship. There are tons of offensive and defensive abiliities that you can obtain in different ways. Try them all out to find your unique playstyle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409000/extras/f35a6ded7dbfe5a0fa7ca156da53484c.poster.avif?t=1699007217\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409000/extras/f35a6ded7dbfe5a0fa7ca156da53484c.webm?t=1699007217\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2409000/extras/f35a6ded7dbfe5a0fa7ca156da53484c.mp4?t=1699007217\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
